#define ANIMESH_STRENGTH 50000
#define STAND "Explosive animation - BAttle Posing"
#define LAND "Explosive animation - Male Crouch Pose 4"
#define WALK "Explosive animation - Walk 11 Power Walk"

#define GREETINGS ["You step onto my canvas with bones that would shatter under their own weight? This won't even be a warm-up.","I smell the fear and frailty on you. Try not to snap your own spine before the bell even rings.","A stiff wind could pin you to the mat, mortal. What delusional sacrifice drove you to face the God of War?","Look at this pathetic frame. I won't even need to draw my sword; a single suplex will turn your frail body to dust.","They send me weaklings who cannot even carry their own armor! Bleed quickly, so I can face a true combatant.","An average mortal steps into the ring. You lift your own weight, but can you carry the crushing burden of a god's wrath?","I’ve slaughtered thousands with your exact build on the battlefields of Sparta. Come, let me break you on the mat.","Standard-issue cannon fodder. Let's see if your blood stains the arena any differently than the rest.","You have the courage of a soldier, but the strength of a peasant. Prepare to be tossed like a ragdoll.","Your perfectly average mechanics will fail the moment I lock in a hold. Welcome to your slaughter.","The absolute pinnacle of mortal conditioning! You'll make a fine trophy when I snap your neck across my knee.","You push your mortal frame to its absolute limits, yet you are still just flesh and bone waiting to be pulverized.","A perfect physical specimen. The snap of your heavily conditioned tendons will be music to my ears.","You've trained your whole life for the arena, pushing your muscle density to the max, just to bleed for my amusement.","You think hoisting twice your weight prepares you for the God of War? I've been breaking 'peak' champions since Troy.","Finally, a combatant who might actually survive the first slam to the canvas! Let the bloodshed begin!","You possess the strength to hurl a chariot, but against me, you're just a heavier punching bag.","Your enhanced muscles reek of false confidence. Let's see how they hold up when I tear them from your bones.","You strike with the force of a battering ram! Good. I was hoping for a wrestling match that would actually make me sweat.","You've stepped beyond human limits, but you're still a long way from Olympus. Come, bleed for me!","A warrior who can shatter stone and bend iron! Step into the center of the ring and let us paint this arena red.","Your brute force is renowned, but can your structural integrity withstand the raw, unbridled fury of war itself?","Now this is a heavyweight bout! Bring that crushing power to the mat, and let's go to war.","You hit with the weight of an entire phalanx. I am going to enjoy breaking you down, piece by piece.","They say you can lift a tank. Let's see if you can lift yourself after I drive you headfirst into the ground.","A titan of the arena! Shake the earth with your heavy steps, mortal, for it will soon be your grave.","I haven't felt a thrill like this since the battle with the Giants! Let our clash tear this ring apart!","Your colossal strength is intoxicating. When I finally pin you, the shockwave will be felt all the way in the Underworld!","You are a true behemoth of devastation. Come, lock arms with the God of War and let's test that vaunted stamina.","This is the violence I crave! Give me your absolute worst, and I will still stand over your broken body laughing!","They call your strength infinite. Excellent. That means I can unleash my true brutality without holding anything back.","A world-breaker steps into my domain! Let the universe tremble as we grapple for absolute supremacy.","Even with strength that defies measure, your blood flows exactly the same. I will spill every drop of it across this canvas.","No limits, no boundaries, just pure, unadulterated violence. This is the match the Fates themselves have prophesied!","You may possess the power to move planets, but against the God of War, you will only find an eternity of agony."]

#define WrestleWin ["Your structural integrity is crumbling under a simple wrist-lock. Try not to weep.","You experience catastrophic muscle fatigue from merely breathing. Why did you even step onto my battlefield?","I barely applied any pressure, yet your fragile joints are already snapping like dry twigs.","Your inverse kinematics are so pathetic you folded into this hold before I even had to pull.","There are absolutely no strength gains to be found in this frail sack of bones. Bleed and be done with it!","An average mortal's muscle fatigue sets in precisely when I start having fun. Suffer for my amusement!","Your physical conditioning is standard, meaning your structural integrity breaks exactly as I anticipated.","You try to fight my hold, but your basic human anatomy simply wasn't forged for war.","I feel your tendons straining against the bone. Will you yield, or let me tear your arm from its socket?","All those mundane strength gains, completely undone by a true Olympian's grip.","The absolute peak of human potential, yet your structural integrity still fails the moment I apply true pressure.","I can smell the lactic acid and muscle fatigue poisoning your veins. Bow to the God of War!","You maximized your mortal strength gains just to be folded in half on the mat by a god.","Perfect conditioning doesn't stop your bones from breaking in my hold. Do you hear them splintering?","You understand leverage and inverse kinematics well for a mortal, but you lack the divine endurance to survive this.","Superhuman? Your structural integrity feels awfully fragile to me right now.","You thought enhanced flesh meant you wouldn't experience muscle fatigue. The God of War teaches harsh lessons.","A decent struggle, but your strength gains have plateaued while my rage is infinite.","I've locked down your limbs. Let's see how much blood I can squeeze from this superhuman frame.","Your desperate resistance only makes the inevitable snap of your spine more satisfying.","You hit with the force of a phalanx, but trapped in this hold, your structural integrity is rapidly deteriorating.","Push back all you want. I live for the moment your titanic muscle fatigue finally breaks your spirit.","Your monstrous strength gains only mean you'll stay conscious longer as I crush your ribs.","I've compromised your inverse kinematics. All that raw, crushing power, completely neutralized by my lock.","Scream for me! Let the arena hear how a heavy-hitter sounds when their body begins to tear apart.","A behemoth brought to his knees! Your massive structural integrity is giving way to sheer divine violence.","Even beasts like you suffer from muscle fatigue eventually. And I will be here, smiling, when you finally break.","You possess the strength to level city walls, yet you cannot break a simple Spartan hold!","I love grappling with titans. The resistance makes the total destruction of your strength gains an absolute joy.","Struggle harder! The more you fight this lock, the more brutally your joints will tear themselves apart.","Incalculable strength? Let's test the true limit of your structural integrity under the crushing grip of Olympus!","World-breaker, your limbs are trembling! Even infinite power falls victim to absolute muscle fatigue against a god.","I have leveraged your own inverse kinematics against you in an inescapable lock. Where are your limitless strength gains now?","You shake the very earth trying to escape, but my hold is absolute. You belong to the God of War!","The universe may fear your might, but I hold you like a squirming child on the canvas. Break for me!"]

#define WrestleDefeat ["You cling to me like a frightened child! Are you trying to wrestle me, or are you just hiding behind my armor?","A pathetic tangle of limbs. I'm letting you hold on just to see if your own exertion snaps your frail neck.","Is this a grappling hold or rigor mortis? You lack the strength to even make me uncomfortable, insect.","You've wrapped yourself around the God of War. Congratulations, you have placed yourself perfectly within range of my teeth.","Hold on tight, weakling. When I stand up, you're coming with me, and the fall alone will break every bone in your body.","A standard infantry lock. I've broken thousands of grunts who tried this exact maneuver on the fields of Troy!","You have basic leverage, mortal, but you lack the killer instinct to finish this. Allow me to demonstrate.","You pin my arm, yet you leave your throat entirely exposed. A fatal error for a common soldier.","Enjoy the dirt while you can. Your human muscles will fatigue, and when they do, I will paint this canvas with your blood.","A brave hold for a mundane mortal. The audacity of it will look wonderful etched onto your tombstone.","You've trained your whole life to lock joints like this. Too bad godhood isn't bound by human ligaments!","A flawless physical technique! I can almost feel the strain. But a peak mortal is still just meat waiting to be carved.","You push your biology to the limit just to keep me down. Let's see how well this hold works when I start snapping your fingers.","You've secured the grapple, champion. Now ask yourself: can you hold down a god of war before your lungs burst?","Impressive leverage. But you brought a wrestling move to a bloodbath. That is your final mistake.","Now we're talking! A hold with some actual teeth! But brute strength won't save you from divine wrath.","You managed to ground me with enhanced mass. Good! The closer we are, the deeper I can drive my blade!","You think securing my limbs means victory? I am the God of War; my entire body is a weapon!","Your superhuman muscles are bulging, desperate to keep me pinned. I'm going to enjoy tearing them off your bones.","A solid lock! But you're sweating, mortal. Your endurance is draining, and my rage is only just igniting.","You possess the raw power to force me to the dirt. Excellent! I love the taste of mud and blood!","A crushing grip! Any lesser deity would yield. But pain only fuels my hunger for your utter destruction!","You wrestle like a beast of burden. Heavy, predictable, and ultimately destined for the slaughterhouse.","You've trapped the God of War in a vice! But a cage is only as strong as its bars, and your flesh is beginning to tear.","Squeeze all you want! Every ounce of pressure you apply only guarantees your death will be infinitely more agonizing.","A titanic hold! You wrestle like the Giants of old, and I will butcher you exactly like I butchered them!","You've forced me to my knees with sheer, catastrophic power. Now let's see if you have the guts to finish the job before I gut you!","My bones are actually groaning under your mass. Glorious! It's been centuries since I felt true pain in the arena!","You hold me down like a collapsing mountain. But the God of War does not succumb to gravity; he conquers it!","A monstrous grapple! But maintaining this will cost you every drop of your stamina, and I have an eternity to outlast you.","Infinite strength, yet you resort to rolling in the dirt! You hold me, but you cannot kill me!","You've pinned me with the weight of the cosmos. Now, watch as I tear my way out of this hold with pure, immortal malice.","My physical form is pinned by your limitless power, but the spirit of war cannot be contained by mere brute force!","You think you've bested me because my shoulders touch the mat? The fight doesn't end until one of us stops breathing, and gods do not suffocate!","Unleash all your incalculable rage to keep me here! It still won't be enough to stop me from ripping your heart out when I break free!"]
